"{\"uid\": \"news18.com-olympics-paris-olympics-2024-adam-peaty-positive-for-covid-after-winning-silver-8983318.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Adam Peaty tested positive for Covid at the Paris Olympics on Monday, the British team said, a day after winning silver in the 100m breaststroke despite apparently feeling under the weather.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 81, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9951034437023296, \"rank\": 0.004096844274847431, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decorated 29-year-old \\\"is hopeful to be back in competition for the relay events later in the swimming programme\\\", according to a Team GB statement.\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999755718821, \"rank\": 2.3788236221820714e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Adam Peaty began feeling unwell on Sunday, ahead of his men's 100m breaststroke final,\\\" it said.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the hours after the final, his symptoms became worse and he was tested for Covid early on Monday morning.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He tested positive at that point.\\\"\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Olympics 2024 Day 3 -LIVE  Peaty, who was the two-time reigning 100m champion, was edged out into second by just 0.02 secs by surprise winner Nicolo Martinenghi of Italy in a thrilling race on Sunday.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"score\": 0.9999999871768069, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolo Martinenghi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\"}, {\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9986651990179275, \"rank\": 0.0006880015025521345, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no suggestion at the time that Peaty was unwell.\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As in any case of illness, the situation is being managed appropriately, with all usual precautions being taken to keep the wider delegation healthy,\\\" Team GB added.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Briton h